{"id": 1689, "genre": 1001, "title": "在参考旅行攻略的时候，你都有哪些避雷针？", "description": "标题里写着“小众冷门目的地”的，等我看到+订票+冲刺过去，也都已经挤成狗了。(题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 1742, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170515151533fxPQTFvNcuApdMr7.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-26T03:00:19Z", "options": [{"id": 207624, "content": "传统景点、高峰期…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001376}, {"id": 207881, "content": "仿古街，一般都是义乌入货翻几倍骗骗游客老外", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 207641, "content": "坚决不跟团", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665515}, {"id": 207901, "content": "对于土特产，去当地的大卖场捕获", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041994}, {"id": 207902, "content": "避开高峰期", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403578}, {"id": 207652, "content": "当地人介绍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340829}, {"id": 207653, "content": "让人满意的推荐餐厅太少", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037321}, {"id": 207913, "content": "真正的当地美食很，还有手艺品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004417}, {"id": 208169, "content": "最头痛的是吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042844}, {"id": 207664, "content": "经典路线……最好看看是不是自己真的喜欢……还有网红吃店，不如走走停停偶遇热闹的路边摊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038442}, {"id": 207666, "content": "跟团", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685253}, {"id": 207667, "content": "跟团", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685253}, {"id": 207668, "content": "我，从来，没有相信过这些攻略", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1033463}, {"id": 208436, "content": "在欧洲一定要背着小包，漫无目的逛老城", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1043382}, {"id": 207925, "content": "攻略稍微一看就好，到个地方就想随便逛一逛，随便吃一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994895}, {"id": 208695, "content": "千万不要看某某推荐的餐馆，当个参考还好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034129}, {"id": 207672, "content": "都是放屁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817373}, {"id": 207675, "content": "冷门文艺去处  果然没什么看头", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149142}, {"id": 207679, "content": "三五个朋友一起旅游 什么都是愉快的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041133}, {"id": 207936, "content": "坚决不跟团", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844640}, {"id": 207684, "content": "看餐厅绝对不去看推荐，宁愿上X团找附近餐厅。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889143}, {"id": 207940, "content": "不跟团不扎堆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042230}, {"id": 219972, "content": "别看太多游记 伤脑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070923}, {"id": 208200, "content": "网红店！门口永远大排长队的店！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902089}, {"id": 207689, "content": "跟着感觉走…从来都是没人开辟的美好地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037005}, {"id": 207945, "content": "在陌生的街上随便走总能找到自己感兴趣的地方 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728511}, {"id": 207691, "content": "千万不要听什么攻略啊之类的，首先要明白旅行是自己的不是别人的，随性一些不必跟签到一样这么程序化，你要领略的是当地的美，而不是为了到点打卡", "image": "img/option/option/20170527090534A4ftZiU3vCgp5Qz6.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 553583}, {"id": 207947, "content": "随意闲逛，自己发现风景", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994334}, {"id": 207693, "content": "在各大社交平台看游记，看最新的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024356}, {"id": 207697, "content": "小吃街 美食街真的是踩雷专区", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 65311}, {"id": 207712, "content": "被推荐的店商业气息已经很浓了 想感受到真正原汁原味的当地风味很难了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041294}, {"id": 203875, "content": "经典线路=参考它们能和三万个同胞撞游", "image": null, "praise_count": 165, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 207459, "content": "节假日出游攻略照片里基本没人，实际你懂的...", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013245}, {"id": 203876, "content": "频频被提到的必吃餐厅，好不好吃不一定，但排长队是一定的", "image": null, "praise_count": 327, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 207972, "content": "当地人常去的地方，其实没几个人去过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288677}, {"id": 207718, "content": "注意去的时候的月份和季节", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946980}, {"id": 207465, "content": "我喜欢先看地图再搜攻略，没什么攻略甚至没有攻略的地方，我就去那里?", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040011}, {"id": 203883, "content": "开篇五百字描述和目的地“相恋经过”的直接pass，再看一小时恐怕还在写值机选座", "image": null, "praise_count": 65, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 207467, "content": "大众点评", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525930}, {"id": 207468, "content": "豆瓣评分", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525930}, {"id": 207470, "content": "最好是有个认识的人，不然真的头大", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040655}, {"id": 207472, "content": "特色小吃街", "image": null, "praise_count": 218, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 734353}, {"id": 207731, "content": "民工民工明明哦名字自由职业者注意休息让我想起以前一直一直以为说着说着说着玩去欣赏欣赏欣赏一下欣赏欣赏欣赏欣赏男朋友早睡早起晚上一起一直以为你是明明说着说着说着玩企业培训师我先去洗澡之前一直以为你明明明敏明明哦明敏公明公共明敏明星嘻嘻嘻嘻这么黑定妆照这样嘻嘻嘻嘻嘻你没事儿厘米秀回", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039791}, {"id": 207477, "content": "冷门博物馆美术馆都是小众好去处", "image": null, "praise_count": 98, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833679}, {"id": 207479, "content": "城隍庙，户部巷，宽窄巷，南京夫子庙，等……等……", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 881427}, {"id": 207736, "content": "OMG下来了", "image": "img/option/option/201705271106251wc6gBrmVlDIx4UM.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041350}, {"id": 207481, "content": "捷径或许会错过好多美丽的风景", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 857633}, {"id": 207482, "content": "一生必去！", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259532}, {"id": 207483, "content": "看别人攻略里踩坑的地方，和着重说不推荐的地方（附带原因）", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684014}, {"id": 207998, "content": "不再所谓的美食街大吃特吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042552}]}